Text: SubscriptionJan Thank you for subscribing to the following Continental Airlines mailing lists COOL Domestic COOL International You are subscribed as With your subscription you will receive FREE emails featuring low fare specials and promotions from Continental Airlines and some of our partners We plan to send notices out every other Tuesday However we cannot guarantee delivery on a specific day due to any unforeseen Internet problems which we have no control over If you have not subscribed in time to get the email for the current week please feel free to visit our website at and click through to the Vacations and Specials tab to view the Specials for the upcoming week If you would like to UNSUBSCRIBE to any of the Continental Airlines mailing lists please click here dashbuilddashaspvs
